/* Changelog Notes - Paladin

	Smite
	Base damage bonus increased from 20% to 40%
	...
	Smite no longer has knockback (except in PvP)

	Zeal
	Added +20% base bonus damage
	Now gains its +20% damage per level bonus from level 1-4 instead of gaining +0%
	Synergies reduced from 20% to 15%

	Holy Shield
	Level 28+ damage scaling increased from 4-4 to 5-5

	Sanctuary
	Added 50% base attack rating
	Added 5% attack rating per level
	Synergies increased from 7% to 8%
	Now has holy sword instead of conversion as a synergy

	Holy Fire												...aura damage values have also changed slightly since they're based on attack damage values
	Added 50% base attack rating
	Added 5% attack rating per level
	Level 1-8 scaling increased from 1-1 to 1-2				...values don't match? verified in-game
	Level 8-16 scaling increased from 3-3 to 3-4
	Level 16-22 scaling increased from 10-10 to 10-12
	Level 22-28 scaling increased from 19-19 to 18-21
	Level 28+ scaling increased from 23-25 to 25-30
	Synergies reduced from 18% to 15%

	Holy Shock
	Added 50% base attack rating
	Added 5% attack rating per level
	Synergies increased from 8% to 9%

	Holy Freeze
	Added 50% base attack rating
	Added 5% attack rating per level

	Holy Sword
	Replaced Conversion with a new skill: Holy Sword
	Allows the paladin to gain parry chance while wielding two handed swords (Similar to Weapon Block)
	Provides the paladin with increased damage to demons and undead
	...
	Parry cap increased from 45% to 50%
	Scaling changed from +1% per level to +2% per level (levels 1-8) and +1% per level (levels 8+)
	...
	Scaling reworked to diminshing returns scaling
	Base parry chance changed to 8%
	Parry chance cap set to 55%

	Sacrifice
	Synergies increased from 20% to 25%
	Lowered the delay for the AoE explosion on monster death

	Joust
	Items that reduce cooldown will now all you to reduce the cooldown below the 1.5 second minimum cooldown				...previously, the tooltip was inaccurate on Alma Negra?

	Charge
	Charge was previously not gaining it's enhanced damage bonus, this has been fixed
	Enhanced damage per level reduced from 30% to 25%
	Synergies reduced from 25% to 20%

*/
